Introduction

1CHU is a South Korean solo act under MOAI Entertainment. They were the first sub-unit of HeyGirls and debuted with the digital single “Oasis” on July 21, 2022. They are also part of the project girl group PUZZLE. They became an independent group after HeyGirls disbanded on December 26, 2023.

On December 23, 2024, MOAI Entertainment announced Sulhee and Chaerin as members of the pre-debut girl group E11iVYN, while also being members of 1CHU.

On February 6, 2025, MOAI Entertainment announced that Sulhee had not renewed her contract with the company, leaving 1CHU and E11iVYN.
